description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Chukcha purrs with a rating of 56, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 168, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 3 for East, Stringalong for South, and Box for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30563-93741-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [168 Votes, Top 10% Score]
